{"tid":231281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鏗鏘集 24-4-2017 點解租樓就唔係「樓奴」？","createTime":"2017-05-06T02:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T06:33:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25103b3ef22a00ea1bdd776c27cff8091a366f33","tid":231281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:27:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>其實我唔係好明乜野為之「樓奴」？<br />\n<br />\n幫業主供30年樓後, 無資產係手, 就唔係「樓奴」？<br />\n收租30年, 租客幫業主供樓, 30年後業主有資產係手, 個業主係「樓奴」？<br />\n<br />\n有無人解釋一下比我聽？</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去片：[url]<a href=\"https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc/[url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F75Y6128tIAc%2F%5Burl%5D&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d36cd3de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc/[url]</a><br />\n<br />\n睇簡介:<br />\n-兩公婆月入十萬<br />\n-堅拒買樓, 話要享受生活為先<br />\n-兩個仔, 兩個工人, 一架車<br />\n-$7K 租錦上路 700呎村屋, 中環返工"},{"pid":"01fd8ddd8b4bf1cc3b374312f9872548430f84ad","tid":231281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:28:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F75Y6128tIAc&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d0ab7233\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb723b93c9a70fae02608b484a11518a4565ead","tid":231281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:37:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cRoS3JcVi0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6cRoS3JcVi0&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=99a3e5d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cRoS3JcVi0</a><br />\n<br />\n第一PAIR仲好笑, <br />\n<br />\n要求月租1萬以下, 地點要係尖沙咀 / 銅鑼灣<br />\n<br />\n個BUDGET 只搵到劏房, 好唔滿意咁話！"},{"pid":"cde39a09b4f9f3ff5e81a095d795cdb4f5c073e3","tid":231281,"uid":20270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F75Y6128tIAc&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d0ab7233\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n月入十皮唔買樓 都可以俾到好嘅生活仔女 供埋佢外國讀書都仲得 自己又嘆 有乜問題"},{"pid":"a36071724c460240b77d6d0cc5a7b22bee0eaa1d","tid":231281,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:45:21.000Z","msg":"負債過多強制勞動就係奴"},{"pid":"9ac1d2f57e09931fc08c06a3ffe80da474e5f72e","tid":231281,"uid":74569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F75Y6128tIAc&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d0ab7233\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n月入十皮唔買樓 都可以俾到好嘅生活仔女 供埋佢外國讀書都仲得 自己又嘆 有乜問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我feel到樓主果陣酸味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，以為覺得有樓先係一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，跟住笑柒人地傻仔<br />\n<br />\n人地依家係買得起不過唔買呀，選擇權係佢地手上<br />\n<br />\n資產唔一定係樓ga"},{"pid":"da7040a303fcbc43d896c826dd25324d75119748","tid":231281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F75Y6128tIAc&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d0ab7233\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n月入十皮唔買樓 都可以俾到好嘅生活仔女 供埋佢外國讀書都仲得 自己又嘆 有乜問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我feel到樓主果陣酸味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，以為覺得有樓先係一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，跟住笑柒人地傻仔<br />\n<br />\n人地依家係買得起不過唔買呀，選擇權係佢地手上<br />\n<br />\n資產唔一定係樓ga</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n酸佢幫業主供樓？<br />\n<br />\n我個層就供完啦, 之前租客幫我供個層賣燃埋<br />\n<br />\n依家我好燃酸你呀屌"},{"pid":"a109808c0270168cdc0ff4864c737e5556fe9e52","tid":231281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F75Y6128tIAc&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d0ab7233\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/75Y6128tIAc</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n月入十皮唔買樓 都可以俾到好嘅生活仔女 供埋佢外國讀書都仲得 自己又嘆 有乜問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我問緊, 乜野叫「樓奴」？<br />\n<br />\n每月比錢租樓, 點解就唔係「樓奴」<br />\n<br />\n點解業主收租, 反而係「樓奴」<br />\n<br />\nlogic係邊？<br />\n<br />\n其實租樓住既人, 係咪偏向智力及理解力低下？"},{"pid":"7a8fd8db32211cdbf8089ff2af438176a5aa838c","tid":231281,"uid":99124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"樓主都係驚宣揚唔買樓呢樣攪到成易下跌姐，冇成交個市跌，有1個以上單位既人好傷嫁，一個成副身家打個2~3折點算"},{"pid":"cc8b9e492be65f2a1eafd731c12c441c789057f8","tid":231281,"uid":99124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主都係驚宣揚唔買樓呢樣攪到成<span style=\"color: red;\">交</span>下跌姐，冇成交個市跌，有1個以上單位既人好傷嫁，一個成副身家打個2~3折點算</blockquote>"},{"pid":"301d1e7a39a05d4e6c180a366c36faf034509f3d","tid":231281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主都係驚宣揚唔買樓呢樣攪到成<span style=\"color: red;\">交</span>下跌姐，冇成交個市跌，有1個以上單位既人好傷嫁，一個成副身家打個2~3折點算</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係問緊, 「樓奴」定義係乜<br />\n<br />\n我係業主, 唔撚駛做野賺錢, 有人幫我供樓, 供完層樓最終都係我既, <br />\n我係樓奴？<br />\n<br />\n租客兩公婆要去做野, 日日返工放工OT, 要交租比我, 租20年層樓都唔係個租客既, 而個租客唔係「樓奴」？<br />\n<br />\nLOGIC係邊到？"},{"pid":"98016419b41050a108f2f181593bc8c63c89c2a3","tid":231281,"uid":74569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:24:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主都係驚宣揚唔買樓呢樣攪到成<span style=\"color: red;\">交</span>下跌姐，冇成交個市跌，有1個以上單位既人好傷嫁，一個成副身家打個2~3折點算</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係問緊, 「樓奴」定義係乜<br />\n<br />\n我係業主, 唔撚駛做野賺錢, 有人幫我供樓, 供完層樓最終都係我既, <br />\n我係樓奴？<br />\n<br />\n租客兩公婆要去做野, 日日返工放工OT, 要交租比我, 租20年層樓都唔係個租客既, 而個租客唔係「樓奴」？<br />\n<br />\nLOGIC係邊到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓奴定義就係你每個月死儲爛儲，跟住好唔容易買到，之後每個月死供爛供，錢又儲唔到，又要擔心樓價跌，失業，經濟唔好銀行call back loan。<br />\n<br />\n你有兩層樓以上就租比人，你死儲爛儲買得一層樓點租比人？住父母度然後租比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？你比條片入面邊度講到日日返工放工OT？你覺得7K一個月租夠你業主做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n資產唔一定係樓ga <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bee28cc204f065f76b2bf11252de2a1156af62d","tid":231281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主都係驚宣揚唔買樓呢樣攪到成<span style=\"color: red;\">交</span>下跌姐，冇成交個市跌，有1個以上單位既人好傷嫁，一個成副身家打個2~3折點算</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係問緊, 「樓奴」定義係乜<br />\n<br />\n我係業主, 唔撚駛做野賺錢, 有人幫我供樓, 供完層樓最終都係我既, <br />\n我係樓奴？<br />\n<br />\n租客兩公婆要去做野, 日日返工放工OT, 要交租比我, 租20年層樓都唔係個租客既, 而個租客唔係「樓奴」？<br />\n<br />\nLOGIC係邊到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓奴定義就係你每個月死儲爛儲，跟住好唔容易買到，之後每個月死供爛供，錢又儲唔到，又要擔心樓價跌，失業，經濟唔好銀行call back loan。<br />\n<br />\n你有兩層樓以上就租比人，你死儲爛儲買得一層樓點租比人？住父母度然後租比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？你比條片入面邊度講到日日返工放工OT？你覺得7K一個月租夠你業主做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n資產唔一定係樓ga <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「每個月死供爛供，錢又儲唔到」？<br />\n節目入面第一PAIR, 咪就係比完租, 錢都儲唔到囉<br />\n<br />\n如果個業主放租比你係7K, 咁佢供緊既錢就係6K或以下<br />\n如果個業主放租比你係20K, 咁佢供緊既錢就係19K或以下<br />\n做到D乜？做到租客幫業主供樓囉"},{"pid":"b1915b91b9c6c701406cd5be014f9b409044bf98","tid":231281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月入十皮唔買樓 都可以俾到好嘅生活仔女 供埋佢外國讀書都仲得 自己又嘆 有乜問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無問題, 業主睇完個節目, <br />\n<br />\n下次加你DOUBLE租金<br />\n<br />\n其實你地係咪唔記得, 業主可以加租？"},{"pid":"81adadc6f295e0c515a83b4fdf2dff98d047de94","tid":231281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每個月死供爛供，錢又儲唔到，又要擔心樓價跌，失業，經濟唔好銀行call back loan。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吓？<br />\n<br />\n原來租客係唔擔心每個月交完租, 錢又儲唔到？<br />\n<br />\n租客係唔擔心樓價升, 業主加租50%？<br />\n<br />\n租客係唔擔心經濟唔好失業, 交唔起租？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fed1a1901202251b776f4e73f7720b3691e6dee","tid":231281,"uid":74569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每個月死供爛供，錢又儲唔到，又要擔心樓價跌，失業，經濟唔好銀行call back loan。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吓？<br />\n<br />\n原來租客係唔擔心每個月交完租, 錢又儲唔到？<br />\n<br />\n租客係唔擔心樓價升, 業主加租50%？<br />\n<br />\n租客係唔擔心經濟唔好失業, 交唔起租？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地10萬一個月，每個月有9萬3洗，依家租樓都係7K，加50%租都係一萬，我想知道佢地點樣擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd65a16a6040b93634f9d398a33e3aa7b8e8e5a","tid":231281,"uid":99124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每個月死供爛供，錢又儲唔到，又要擔心樓價跌，失業，經濟唔好銀行call back loan。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吓？<br />\n<br />\n原來租客係唔擔心每個月交完租, 錢又儲唔到？<br />\n<br />\n租客係唔擔心樓價升, 業主加租50%？<br />\n<br />\n租客係唔擔心經濟唔好失業, 交唔起租？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地10萬一個月，每個月有9萬3洗，依家租樓都係7K，加50%租都係一萬，我想知道佢地點樣擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講擔心，不如擔心用完比100萬首期，買300萬樓，樓市逆轉，跌剩1/3，錢就冇哂，仲要差銀行200萬，其他朋友到時就用三幾千交租住大單位，自己就要比成萬蚊供個蚊型負家產"},{"pid":"d31b7a2fe528bd3cf4e7cfaeb212684a2436b93b","tid":231281,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cRoS3JcVi0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6cRoS3JcVi0&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=99a3e5d9